    <item>
      <title>彭斯称特朗普应维持 TikTok 禁令，允许美国钢铁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/pence-says-trump-should-uphold-tiktok-ban-allow-us-steel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前副总统迈克·彭斯呼吁他的前任老板支持以国家安全为由禁止 TikTok 的法律，并允许日本新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司以支持全球商业联系，这两种立场都更符合共和党的传统正统观念。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/pence-says-trump-should-uphold-tiktok-ban-allow-us-steel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 DOGE 为亿万富翁设置了利益冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/musk-s-doge-sets-up-conflict-of-interest-clash-for-billionaire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统签署行政命令成立政府效率部，使亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克受到利益冲突法的约束，同时也授予他访问大量具有不可估量价值的联邦数据的权限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/musk-s-doge-sets-up-conflict-of-interest-clash-for-billionaire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟希望于 2 月 1 日恢复监控加沙拉法口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-looks-to-resume-monitoring-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-on-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧盟最高外交官将于周一要求欧盟各国外交部长同意在 2 月 1 日之前恢复欧盟在加沙和埃及之间拉法口岸的边境援助团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-looks-to-resume-monitoring-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-on-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索马里确认埃及将参加当地维和部队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/somalia-confirms-egypt-to-take-part-in-local-peacekeeping-force</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里表示，已与埃及就开罗参与非洲联盟领导的非洲之角国家维和部队完成了技术讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/somalia-confirms-egypt-to-take-part-in-local-peacekeeping-force</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永哲被起诉后面临的法律风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/south-korea-s-yoon-is-indicted-what-s-next-for-impeachment-and-criminal-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正经历一场前所未有的政治危机，其总统面临一项可能导致其下台的法律诉讼和另一项可能导致其死刑的法律诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/south-korea-s-yoon-is-indicted-what-s-next-for-impeachment-and-criminal-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 09:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利让步，欧盟将延长对俄罗斯制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟将于周一因俄罗斯与乌克兰的战争而延长对俄罗斯的制裁，匈牙利准备取消对此举的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/eu-set-to-agree-to-extend-russia-sanctions-hungary-to-back-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:04:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
